    "title": "Marico is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Senior)",
    "description": "Marico has an exciting opening for a Quality Control Engineer at our Jodhpur office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Marico:\nMarico is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Marico!",
